Package: split200str
Type: Package
Title: Split Text Strings Exceeding 200 Characters into Multiple Variables
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Longfei", "LI", , "longfei2.li@sanofi.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This is not an official package. 
             It is merely intended to assist those who have read the PharmaSUG article 
             "An R Function to Split Text Strings Exceeding 200 Characters into Multiple Variables" 
             in gaining a deeper understanding of the R function, using it with ease, and reviewing its source code.
